侵害中国公民生命财产安全的行为，尽快释放全部中国籍电信网络诈骗犯罪嫌疑人。缅北电诈重要头目明国平、明菊兰、明珍珍被成功缉拿归案"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8bb5294d4f636a95ffeffa68472227af_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/630425466"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7If/pYn3wtk/EAMaCTEwMjM3MzIwMCCq5deqBjAAOIQXQApyCTYzMDQyNTQ2NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1700190332.652654", "card_id": "Q_630443741", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 70}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "每天上班为了什么？最期望什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为了不与世界脱轨，"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-67692978d0b015a31d7d6efd0f231ad9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/630443741"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7If/pYn3wtk/EAMaCTEwMjM3NzIyOCCmidiqBjAAOFRAC3IJNjMwNDQzNzQxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1700190332.653382", "card_id": "Q_627879267", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么原生的 macOS 只能安装在苹果设备上？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有些大佬提到了黑苹果，听说过，但没折腾过。在此，补充一下问题，我说的 macOS 指的是官方的，不是指其它手段装上的 macOS。不过我其实也不清楚那些 macOS 和官方相比有啥区别。 据说是硬件差异导致的无法直接安装，具体有哪些差异呢？ 反过来，为什么 Windows 系统可以安装在苹果电脑上呢？不过虽然装的上，但好像也得借